==Drug registration in Hong Kong ==
Under the Pharmacy and Poisons Ordinance (Chapter 138), the Department of Health's Drug Office is responsible for drug registration in Hong Kong. All [[drugs]] sold in Hong Kong are required to be registered with a number, which consists of the prefix 'HK' followed by five digits (e.g. HK-05628).<ref>http://www.psdh.gov.hk/eps/webpage.jsp</ref>
